name: Alina Becker [japp_leack] ^_< -★  (LoRA)
description:
Hi !! („• ֊ •„)੭ I bring you yet again another Instagram Cosplayer https://www.instagram.com/japp_leack/

As per request @qs7 Thank you so much for requesting her she's beautiful (´｡• ◡ •｡`) ♡ !!

So again this model works well with both Photorealistic models and Anime models (sorta).

I used cosplay and Irl photos in the dataset. So go wild with hair colors and eye colors hehe (˵ •̀ ᴗ - ˵ ).

Please be kind with this Lora ♡

modelVersions.name: Alina_Becker_V1
modelVersions.description:
I highly recommend using the trigger word Alina_Becker.

((0.5-1 weight))

I had ALOT of trouble using the Inpaint face fix technique. Im not sure why but it doesnt look like her at all when i use it so i recommend against using it.

Here are all the settings used for most the examples:

Size: 520x520

Denoising strength: 0.68

Clip skip: 2

Steps: 24

Sampler: DPM++ SDE Karras OR Unipc

CFG scale: 7

Upscaler: SwinIR 4x

upscale: 2

For anime models I recommend using the same Base prompt I used for the sample images as the results may vary with certain prompts.
